snippet.title: Snakebird Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Noumenon Games are proud to present Snakebird, a puzzle game about snakebirds and fruits, lots and lots of fruit.
Coming to Steam May 4th, for Windows, Mac and Linux. (Out now!)
http://store.steampowered.com/app/357300/
